{
  "name": "Eye Spy",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "modules/pf1spheres/assets/icons/spheres/scout.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Perception 10 ranks, Scout sphere (Great Senses).</p>\n<p>As a full-round action, you may concentrate on any creature that you successfully used the scout ability on within a number of miles equal to your ranks in Perception. You perceive that creature&#8217;s surroundings as if you were standing where that creature was. While you may use that scouted creature&#8217;s special senses (i.e. darkvision, etc.) you must use your own Perception skill if attempting a check.</p>\n",
